c0000000
00:00:02.170 --> 00:00:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
Thought so.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:03.830 --> 00:00:05.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know an adventurer
when I see one.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A thrilling profession
you've got.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I once hoped
to join your ranks.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:13.220 --> 00:00:14.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess that's what kids do.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:17.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dream big, foolish dreams
that always fall flat.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:55.450 --> 00:01:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:58.700 --> 00:01:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
When I was younger,</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:00.750 --> 00:02:02.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I played sidekick to a friend</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who used to go on all sorts
of little adventures.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:07.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Foolhardy and with energy
to spare,</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:07.800 --> 00:02:10.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he was like a gorilla
trapped in the body of a kid.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:11.210 --> 00:02:13.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That said, he was a good kid</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:14.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who always cared
for his friends.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:17.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As we grew up,</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:17.810 --> 00:02:20.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I forgot our dreams
of braving the unknown.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:21.770 --> 00:02:23.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until he invited me
to join his party</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:23.850 --> 00:02:25.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and become the real thing.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:27.610 --> 00:02:29.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder how different
my life would be</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I had only taken
his hand back then.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:33.900 --> 00:02:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been ten years now
since that happened,</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:36.790 --> 00:02:38.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I regret it to this day.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:39.830 --> 00:02:40.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:41.410 --> 00:02:43.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And why exactly are you
sharing this with me?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:47.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, my village's
harvest festival is coming up.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:48.300 --> 00:02:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My brother sent me
into the woods</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:52.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to find some herbs for cooking,
which should've been no issue.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:53.210 --> 00:02:55.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you see...
[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:56.470 --> 00:02:58.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fell in a bottomless swamp,
and it became one.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:00.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hear me out.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:00.810 --> 00:03:03.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My biggest regret
was not taking his hand.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:03.850 --> 00:03:04.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, please,</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:07.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't let yours
be not taking mine.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:07.860 --> 00:03:09.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have a chance
to change my fate, here.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:11.020 --> 00:03:13.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just give me a moment.
I need to think.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:14.190 --> 00:03:16.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? You're messing with me.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:16.580 --> 00:03:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's so confusing it requires
that much thought?</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:18.870 --> 00:03:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Your hand is dirty.
-[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:20.780 --> 00:03:22.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna drown in this muck!</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:24.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can wash your hands off
later, can't you?</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:25.250 --> 00:03:26.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And besides, miss,</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:27.790 --> 00:03:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to a certain extent,</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:31.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we grown-ups
are dirty by nature.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:32.210 --> 00:03:33.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:33.500 --> 00:03:34.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've met countless adults,</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but none quite
as filthy as you.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:38.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must ask you for more time.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:39.260 --> 00:03:40.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you would let me think,</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:40.390 --> 00:03:42.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might recall the spell
to pull you out.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:42.850 --> 00:03:45.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Got it. But could we
pick up the pace a bit?</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:45.690 --> 00:03:46.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me see.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:47.610 --> 00:03:48.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:49.230 --> 00:03:50.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you have any luck
finding herbs?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:51.060 --> 00:03:52.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. I remember.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:52.980 --> 00:03:53.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:59.410 --> 00:04:00.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can take it from here,
thanks.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:00.910 --> 00:04:02.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're so welcome.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry for the trouble
my mistress caused.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:06.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, I'm in no spot
to complain.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your friend there
saved my life.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps. But regardless,
I will scold her later.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:12.290 --> 00:04:13.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My night off.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:15.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you folks sure
you don't need to stop</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:15.550 --> 00:04:16.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the village before you go?</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:17.300 --> 00:04:18.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're busy preparing
for the festival,</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:19.090 --> 00:04:21.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'd like to find
some way to say thanks.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:21.590 --> 00:04:23.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're hoping to reach
a larger town today.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:24.140 --> 00:04:26.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our supplies are low, so we
need a good place to restock.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:27.060 --> 00:04:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:28.350 --> 00:04:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, in that case, be careful.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:30.350 --> 00:04:32.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are a lot of dangerous
venomous creatures</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:33.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>out there in those woods.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-Good to know.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:40.490 --> 00:04:41.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:45.540 --> 00:04:46.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, something just bit me.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:47.290 --> 00:04:49.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? You have to be kidding.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:49.540 --> 00:04:50.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were told
to be on the lookout</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for that sort of danger
mere moments ago.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:53.370 --> 00:04:55.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First things first,
let's bandage the wound.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:56.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Uh-oh.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:57.470 --> 00:04:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My nose might be
bleeding a little.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:04.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any spell that has to do
with identifying poison</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:04.220 --> 00:05:06.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>falls into a priest's realm,
so I'm no help.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:06.770 --> 00:05:08.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't recognize
this reaction,</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:10.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so the antidotes we have
might not do the job.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:11.350 --> 00:05:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should get you checked
at a church to be safe.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, Fern. For how much longer
can you use your flying magic?</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:17.780 --> 00:05:19.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would say we only have
about 30 minutes,</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:20.070 --> 00:05:21.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since it consumes
a lot of mana.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:22.030 --> 00:05:24.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unfortunately, that won't
get us all the way to the town.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:25.290 --> 00:05:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll have to head back
to that village.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:27.290 --> 00:05:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Leave moving the patient to me.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:29.290 --> 00:05:30.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's really
not that big a deal.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:31.460 --> 00:05:32.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna be fine, trust me.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:33.290 --> 00:05:35.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My master taught me that
the best way to beat poisons</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:35.550 --> 00:05:36.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is to just tough 'em out.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:37.300 --> 00:05:38.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come to think of it,</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:39.300 --> 00:05:41.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have seen Eisen take
several poison-coated arrows</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:43.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the back and be fine.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:43.670 --> 00:05:45.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was enough
to knock out a dragon.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:46.140 --> 00:05:47.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heiter was appalled.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:49.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You get it!
-No.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:50.270 --> 00:05:52.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only thing that
tale proves is Mister Eisen</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:52.730 --> 00:05:54.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is very far from normal.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:55.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's more,</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:55.990 --> 00:05:57.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Master Heiter would
always remind me</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:58.360 --> 00:05:59.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>poison's the cause
of 20 percent</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:00.030 --> 00:06:01.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of adventurer deaths.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:01.990 --> 00:06:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should hurry.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:08.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why? This is complete overkill!</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:13.500 --> 00:06:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN'S BROTHER]
I'm afraid you're too late.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:15.630 --> 00:06:18.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A few hours from now,
his brain will start to melt.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:18.340 --> 00:06:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At that point,
it will flow from his nose,</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:21.300 --> 00:06:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then he'll die.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:22.590 --> 00:06:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's terrifying!</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please guide us, Father.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:27.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There must be something
we can do for him.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:27.890 --> 00:06:29.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That bite was deadly,</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:29.180 --> 00:06:30.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and could typically
only be cured</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:32.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if treated immediately.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But perhaps my brother
will be able to help you.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:35.780 --> 00:06:37.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There you are.
We have a problem, brother.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:40.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We both agree this new tub
is too small, right?</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:40.900 --> 00:06:42.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's honor in poverty.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:43.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure, to a point, maybe.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:44.610 --> 00:06:46.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But impoverishing down to a tub</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:48.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fit for fingertips
seems extreme.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:48.830 --> 00:06:50.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have greater concerns.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:50.790 --> 00:06:52.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a look at this boy
for me, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:53.290 --> 00:06:55.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.
These are the adventurers</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:55.210 --> 00:06:56.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was telling you about.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:57.130 --> 00:06:58.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're the folks
who rescued me.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:00.590 --> 00:07:01.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at you.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:02.050 --> 00:07:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were bitten
by a snake, huh?</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:04.300 --> 00:07:05.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Glad you took
my warning to heart.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:08.850 --> 00:07:09.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:10.390 --> 00:07:11.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:11.810 --> 00:07:14.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There. Consider my debt repaid.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:15.070 --> 00:07:17.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So long. I'm going
to help out at the plaza.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:19.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not bleeding.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:23.070 --> 00:07:24.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And there's no brains.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:25.370 --> 00:07:27.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems the effects
of the poison are gone.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:27.580 --> 00:07:29.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaks and slams]</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:30.580 --> 00:07:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, Father. Is he...</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:33.620 --> 00:07:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's my little brother,</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:35.630 --> 00:07:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and quite the priest.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] That holy symbol
around your neck.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:42.630 --> 00:07:44.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's awarded to the most
outstanding priest</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:44.710 --> 00:07:46.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a region
by the holy capital.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:47.850 --> 00:07:50.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your brother came in
and instantly cured a poison</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:50.350 --> 00:07:52.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a top-level healing expert
called incurable.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:54.220 --> 00:07:56.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's no less than a genius.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:56.650 --> 00:07:58.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a feeling
you of all people</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:58.400 --> 00:07:59.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would notice, Miss Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:00.020 --> 00:08:01.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't realize
you knew who I was.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:02.150 --> 00:08:05.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Heiter told me
many a story about you.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:06.780 --> 00:08:08.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's who gave me this.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:08.370 --> 00:08:10.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He came from the capital
to observe us,</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:10.490 --> 00:08:12.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I suppose he thought
I was doing rather well.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:13.780 --> 00:08:16.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, I'm still just
a provincial priest</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:16.460 --> 00:08:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a small village.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:17.630 --> 00:08:20.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This medallion
is my greatest achievement,</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:20.330 --> 00:08:22.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and while I'm very proud,
the truth is,</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:23.290 --> 00:08:25.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my ability doesn't even
compare to Sein's.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:28.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see, we lost our parents.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:08:28.510 --> 00:08:30.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was just a child
when it happened.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:08:31.340 --> 00:08:33.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I was young myself
when they passed away,</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:34.140 --> 00:08:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I raised my brother.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:36.690 --> 00:08:37.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When he was little,</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:41.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he would often talk about
becoming an adventurer someday.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:45.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He didn't want to grow up to be
an ordinary village priest,</b></Default>

c0000173
00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:46.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because he couldn't bear
for all his days</b></Default>

c0000174
00:08:46.990 --> 00:08:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to look the same
the way that mine do.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:08:50.530 --> 00:08:51.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He would tell me that</b></Default>

c0000176
00:08:51.610 --> 00:08:53.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with eyes full
of hopes and dreams.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:08:54.950 --> 00:08:56.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That shine has dimmed now.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:08:56.580 --> 00:08:59.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As he becomes more like me
each passing year,</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:00.040 --> 00:09:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>his soul is aching
for something greater.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:04.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, please...</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:05.260 --> 00:09:07.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>take my brother with you
on your journey</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and away from this village.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:09.010 --> 00:09:11.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's perfect.
You clearly need a priest,</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:11.510 --> 00:09:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I'm certain
he needs someone</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:12.970 --> 00:09:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to give him that final push.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:17.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:17.980 --> 00:09:20.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Come on, Frieren.
He's an easy yes!</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:20.890 --> 00:09:23.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The man's a genius.
What is there to think about?</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000190
00:09:24.730 --> 00:09:27.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever it is, it can't be
worth risking my brains</b></Default>

c0000191
00:09:27.150 --> 00:09:28.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>coming out of my nose again.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:09:29.110 --> 00:09:30.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He would make things safer.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:09:30.780 --> 00:09:33.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And our journey's headed deeper
into the unknown from here.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you acting so wary,
Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

c0000196
00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:41.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An aversion to my own kind,
I suppose.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I don't know what
that's supposed to mean.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:46.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't care.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:09:46.090 --> 00:09:47.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm inviting him
whether you like it or not.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:09:51.420 --> 00:09:52.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where's he going?</b></Default>

c0000201
00:09:52.670 --> 00:09:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe the bar downstairs?</b></Default>

c0000202
00:09:54.470 --> 00:09:57.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get the feeling Mister Sein
spends a lot of time there.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:09:57.980 --> 00:09:59.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Of course.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:02.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Alcohol.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:10:03.850 --> 00:10:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tobacco.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:10:06.150 --> 00:10:07.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gambling.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:10:09.530 --> 00:10:11.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So at what point does
corrupt become depraved?</b></Default>

c0000208
00:10:12.280 --> 00:10:14.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just getting to know
my fellow man.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:10:14.990 --> 00:10:16.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Care to join us, kid?</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The name is Stark,</b></Default>

c0000211
00:10:18.950 --> 00:10:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I came to ask you
to join us.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:10:21.580 --> 00:10:23.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are looking for a priest.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:10:23.250 --> 00:10:25.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
That's a funny joke,</b></Default>

c0000214
00:10:26.050 --> 00:10:28.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm already
a priest for the village.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:10:28.710 --> 00:10:30.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't go adventuring.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:10:32.010 --> 00:10:33.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:10:33.710 --> 00:10:34.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This could be fun.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:10:36.600 --> 00:10:37.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a load off, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:10:38.390 --> 00:10:40.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you can beat me at a hand,
I'll join your party.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:10:40.930 --> 00:10:41.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you for real?</b></Default>

c0000221
00:10:42.060 --> 00:10:43.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man of the cloth and my word.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:10:44.100 --> 00:10:45.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000223
00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] [laughing]
Please don't do this!</b></Default>

c0000224
00:10:50.230 --> 00:10:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:53.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I just heard
Mister Stark</b></Default>

c0000226
00:10:53.280 --> 00:10:54.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yell from downstairs.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:10:57.660 --> 00:11:00.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000228
00:11:00.490 --> 00:11:02.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunting]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000229
00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like someone
robbed him blind!</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:06.550 --> 00:11:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How awful.
Who would do such a thing?</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:09.550 --> 00:11:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SEIN] No hard feelings.
-[both gasp]</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:11.670 --> 00:11:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:13.050 --> 00:11:16.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We grown-ups are dirty,
and we play dirty, too.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:11:16.810 --> 00:11:18.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone's robbed him
blind, too!</b></Default>

c0000235
00:11:18.930 --> 00:11:21.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That someone would be
the village chief.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:11:21.140 --> 00:11:23.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The tyrant's got
Lady Luck on a leash.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:11:23.810 --> 00:11:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sein.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:27.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hear that you're
looking for a priest.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:11:27.570 --> 00:11:28.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look elsewhere.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:31.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want to become
an adventurer, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000241
00:11:31.980 --> 00:11:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a massive difference
between want and wanted.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:11:35.110 --> 00:11:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's too late for me now.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:11:36.660 --> 00:11:38.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See, I should've left
when there was a chance</b></Default>

c0000244
00:11:39.080 --> 00:11:40.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could've actually found him.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:11:41.370 --> 00:11:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if that's not enough,</b></Default>

c0000246
00:11:43.240 --> 00:11:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>now I don't even have
the wardrobe for it.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:11:48.540 --> 00:11:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Frieren. Defeat the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:11:51.290 --> 00:11:52.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Join our party.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:11:52.630 --> 00:11:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It's too late for me.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:11:54.920 --> 00:11:58.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been over 500 years now
since I last fought a demon.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:11:59.050 --> 00:12:01.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're battles I've
long forgotten how to win.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:05.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I deferred that decision
for centuries too long.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:12:06.400 --> 00:12:08.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I missed the moment
this adventure</b></Default>

c0000254
00:12:08.150 --> 00:12:09.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would've made sense for me.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:12:10.770 --> 00:12:13.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Probably because I was
far too cowardly to face him.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:12:14.940 --> 00:12:16.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
None of that matters, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:20.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't dwell on the past
when you have the present.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:12:23.070 --> 00:12:27.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000259
00:12:27.460 --> 00:12:28.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000260
00:12:30.380 --> 00:12:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Find someone else.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:12:32.460 --> 00:12:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't have any idea
how I feel.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:12:35.000 --> 00:12:37.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please. Your reaction tells me.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:12:38.260 --> 00:12:40.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And frankly, I couldn't
like you less, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:43.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]
Great.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:12:44.300 --> 00:12:45.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Well, in that case--
-So I've decided</b></Default>

c0000266
00:12:45.850 --> 00:12:47.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're going to join us,
no matter what.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:12:49.100 --> 00:12:50.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? But why?</b></Default>

c0000268
00:12:52.770 --> 00:12:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes so little sense
it's scary.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:12:56.070 --> 00:12:57.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You saved me.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:12:57.610 --> 00:12:58.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So toasty.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:00.570 --> 00:13:03.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I'm truly sorry for all
the trouble that we caused you.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:03.740 --> 00:13:05.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please excuse us.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:05.870 --> 00:13:06.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:07.250 --> 00:13:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How much did it cost
to get everything back?</b></Default>

c0000275
00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:11.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said we should
take our time</b></Default>

c0000276
00:13:11.370 --> 00:13:13.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and enjoy the harvest festival,</b></Default>

c0000277
00:13:13.540 --> 00:13:15.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then he gave it all
back to me for free.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:17.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A nice man.
It's your lucky day.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:13:18.220 --> 00:13:20.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said he didn't know
what to do with the axe.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:21.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's kinda sad.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:13:22.510 --> 00:13:24.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, Mister Stark.
Put these on.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:26.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How rude!
Do you have to hold them</b></Default>

c0000283
00:13:27.060 --> 00:13:28.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like they're too gross
for your precious hands?</b></Default>

c0000284
00:13:29.230 --> 00:13:31.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I believe these
are yours, Mister Sein.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:13:31.850 --> 00:13:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fluttering]</b></Default>

c0000286
00:13:34.350 --> 00:13:35.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000287
00:13:35.570 --> 00:13:38.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, someone's grumpy.
What'd I do to set her off?</b></Default>

c0000288
00:13:39.280 --> 00:13:40.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For starters,
you robbed poor Stark</b></Default>

c0000289
00:13:40.950 --> 00:13:42.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of all his possessions.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] I told you that
wasn't me. It was the chief.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:13:47.250 --> 00:13:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] People who gamble
are the lowest of the low.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:13:50.250 --> 00:13:51.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get it. I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:54.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And to think that man's
supposed to be a priest.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:13:55.250 --> 00:13:57.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any priest who drinks
is wrong in my book.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:13:58.130 --> 00:14:00.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Mistress Frieren.
A priest once told me</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:00.970 --> 00:14:03.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that alcohol
is the very best medicine.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:06.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] How dare Heiter
poison your young mind.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:07.520 --> 00:14:10.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless of whether he
decides to come with us or not,</b></Default>

c0000299
00:14:10.930 --> 00:14:13.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do feel that Sein should
become an adventurer.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:14:13.930 --> 00:14:16.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That idea has really grown
on you since this all began.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:14:17.900 --> 00:14:19.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I realized that
it might be nice</b></Default>

c0000302
00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:21.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to give someone
the push they need,</b></Default>

c0000303
00:14:22.070 --> 00:14:24.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just like Himmel the Hero
gave to me.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:14:25.540 --> 00:14:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000305
00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:30.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] For whatever
reason, the adventurers</b></Default>

c0000306
00:14:30.660 --> 00:14:31.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>decided to hang around.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:14:32.660 --> 00:14:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Their presence has taken up
more than a bit of space.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:14:35.800 --> 00:14:39.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000309
00:14:39.800 --> 00:14:41.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They've been trying
to recruit me</b></Default>

c0000310
00:14:41.550 --> 00:14:43.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>every day since their arrival.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:14:43.630 --> 00:14:47.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000312
00:14:47.220 --> 00:14:49.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've tried my best
to make them stop,</b></Default>

c0000313
00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:51.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but my efforts
have been in vain.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:14:52.100 --> 00:14:54.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They invite me on adventures
with cheer in their voices</b></Default>

c0000315
00:14:54.770 --> 00:14:57.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and eyes full of hopes
and dreams.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:14:58.110 --> 00:14:59.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like he did back then.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:00.780 --> 00:15:02.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GORILLA WARRIOR]
The plan is to travel around</b></Default>

c0000318
00:15:02.110 --> 00:15:03.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Northern Lands for a bit.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:15:04.900 --> 00:15:06.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be back
around the harvest,</b></Default>

c0000320
00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>three years from now.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:15:07.990 --> 00:15:09.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you aren't ready
to hit the road yet,</b></Default>

c0000322
00:15:09.990 --> 00:15:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you can join me then.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:15:12.120 --> 00:15:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go on our next
adventure together.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:15:16.550 --> 00:15:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Every time
they try to recruit me,</b></Default>

c0000325
00:15:19.130 --> 00:15:20.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder, why now?</b></Default>

c0000326
00:15:21.960 --> 00:15:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They radiate hope too bright
for my tired eyes.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:15:27.350 --> 00:15:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN'S BROTHER] You want
to know what Sein likes?</b></Default>

c0000328
00:15:29.640 --> 00:15:30.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For what?</b></Default>

c0000329
00:15:30.720 --> 00:15:32.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can't seem to win him over,</b></Default>

c0000330
00:15:32.760 --> 00:15:34.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we're looking for ideas.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:15:34.430 --> 00:15:36.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does my brother like?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:15:36.270 --> 00:15:39.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alcohol, tobacco, and gambling
always seem to attract him.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:15:39.230 --> 00:15:40.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've gathered that much.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:15:40.900 --> 00:15:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're sure
this guy is a priest?</b></Default>

c0000335
00:15:42.980 --> 00:15:44.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Master Heiter
was in good company.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:15:44.900 --> 00:15:46.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All serious priests
like to drink.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:15:47.910 --> 00:15:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure that I've met
a serious priest.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:15:50.580 --> 00:15:51.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me see.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:15:52.620 --> 00:15:55.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What he adores more
than anything is older women.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:15:55.160 --> 00:15:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How fitting
of our depraved priest.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:15:57.250 --> 00:15:59.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Older ladies, huh?
Thank you,</b></Default>

c0000342
00:16:00.170 --> 00:16:03.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm not entirely sure what
to do with that information.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:16:05.040 --> 00:16:06.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm? Hello?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:10.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, that's right.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:16:10.180 --> 00:16:11.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're kidding me.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:16:11.390 --> 00:16:13.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This sickle is too small
to use, don't you think?</b></Default>

c0000347
00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:15.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can hardly cut grass.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:16:16.150 --> 00:16:18.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, it's you three again.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:20.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000350
00:16:21.270 --> 00:16:22.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Do you have a minute, Sein?</b></Default>

c0000351
00:16:22.690 --> 00:16:23.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're still here?</b></Default>

c0000352
00:16:24.020 --> 00:16:25.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:16:25.660 --> 00:16:27.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm getting sick
of repeating myself, kid.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:16:27.910 --> 00:16:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Find someone else.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:16:30.490 --> 00:16:31.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:35.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't you like to travel
with an older lady on your arm?</b></Default>

c0000357
00:16:35.670 --> 00:16:37.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at who you're talking to.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:39.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The thought of that
very scenario was why</b></Default>

c0000359
00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to be an adventurer
in the first place.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:16:42.420 --> 00:16:43.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What a motive.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:16:43.630 --> 00:16:45.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
I'm on the edge of my seat.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:16:45.760 --> 00:16:47.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is this vixen
of which you speak?</b></Default>

c0000363
00:16:48.260 --> 00:16:49.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've been looking
right at her, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:16:50.930 --> 00:16:52.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you realize I'm an elf?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:16:52.640 --> 00:16:55.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As far as older women go,
I'm as old as you can get.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:16:56.060 --> 00:16:57.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000367
00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:58.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew you were an elf.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:16:59.060 --> 00:17:00.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think my brother
mentioned that.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:17:01.730 --> 00:17:02.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:17:05.190 --> 00:17:06.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're too cruel.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:17:06.570 --> 00:17:08.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She hardly looks like a woman,
let alone older!</b></Default>

c0000372
00:17:09.030 --> 00:17:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He seems so distressed.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:12.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I apologize.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:17:13.110 --> 00:17:15.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had no desire
to take it to this level,</b></Default>

c0000375
00:17:15.200 --> 00:17:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you leave me no choice.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:17:18.500 --> 00:17:21.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The time has come to use
the ancient seduction technique</b></Default>

c0000377
00:17:21.580 --> 00:17:23.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>taught to me my master.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:17:24.170 --> 00:17:25.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mwah.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:17:25.250 --> 00:17:27.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000380
00:17:30.800 --> 00:17:32.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh, what was that?
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:17:33.380 --> 00:17:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I blew you a kiss, of course.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:17:35.340 --> 00:17:37.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe you're too young
to appreciate it, sonny.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:17:37.890 --> 00:17:41.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Somebody!
Take this twisted child home!</b></Default>

c0000384
00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:43.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was way too steamy for me.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:17:43.310 --> 00:17:44.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
What's the deal with you two?</b></Default>

c0000386
00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:46.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That's odd.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:17:46.490 --> 00:17:48.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I tried the very
same maneuver on Himmel,</b></Default>

c0000388
00:17:48.570 --> 00:17:50.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it knocked him out cold.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:17:51.820 --> 00:17:52.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000390
00:17:53.780 --> 00:17:54.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Himmel!</b></Default>

c0000391
00:17:55.030 --> 00:17:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
You are a wicked woman.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:17:57.540 --> 00:17:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-How bizarre.
-I'm with you.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I had been the target
of your attack,</b></Default>

c0000394
00:18:01.910 --> 00:18:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would've been
in grave danger.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:18:03.410 --> 00:18:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As depraved as he is,
he's still a holy man.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:18:05.920 --> 00:18:07.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And a formidable foe.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:18:07.220 --> 00:18:08.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SEIN] That's enough already.
-[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000398
00:18:09.590 --> 00:18:12.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not becoming
an adventurer, so quit.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:18:12.840 --> 00:18:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I thought that you wanted
to go after your friend.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:18:16.850 --> 00:18:18.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You understand
my reason, brother.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:18:19.810 --> 00:18:20.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do I, Sein?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:18:21.810 --> 00:18:24.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He promised me that he would
be back here in three years.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:27.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He hasn't been back for ten.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:18:28.650 --> 00:18:31.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The obvious explanation
is that he's dead.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:18:34.190 --> 00:18:35.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you're going to give up</b></Default>

c0000406
00:18:35.320 --> 00:18:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without ever going
to look for him?</b></Default>

c0000407
00:18:39.160 --> 00:18:41.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ten years isn't as long
as you think.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:18:41.830 --> 00:18:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The more time that you wait,</b></Default>

c0000409
00:18:43.080 --> 00:18:45.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the greater and greater
that number will grow.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:18:46.170 --> 00:18:47.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll wonder if you
could've made it</b></Default>

c0000411
00:18:47.710 --> 00:18:49.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you had left town with us.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:18:50.840 --> 00:18:51.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
It's too...</b></Default>

c0000413
00:18:52.170 --> 00:18:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Too late, you suppose, correct?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:18:56.140 --> 00:18:57.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't dwell in the past</b></Default>

c0000415
00:18:57.600 --> 00:18:59.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you have
the present, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:19:03.350 --> 00:19:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000417
00:19:05.310 --> 00:19:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't go.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:19:06.860 --> 00:19:08.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Couldn't then, can't now.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:19:08.440 --> 00:19:10.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been ten years, and I
still have the same reason.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:19:12.070 --> 00:19:14.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not so much that
I would miss this village.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:17.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't leave
my brother behind.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:19:17.660 --> 00:19:20.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're scared of leaving me?
Why is that?</b></Default>

c0000423
00:19:21.870 --> 00:19:24.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When Mister Heiter came
to observe us years ago,</b></Default>

c0000424
00:19:24.740 --> 00:19:26.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard you both talking.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:19:28.170 --> 00:19:30.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] Your talent could
take you far, my lad.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:32.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no doubt you
could serve as a priest</b></Default>

c0000427
00:19:32.130 --> 00:19:33.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the holy capital.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:19:33.460 --> 00:19:35.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN'S BROTHER]
Me, in the holy capital?</b></Default>

c0000429
00:19:36.010 --> 00:19:38.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, without question.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:19:38.390 --> 00:19:40.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That sounds great,
but what would happen</b></Default>

c0000431
00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:42.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to my little brother
if I chose to go?</b></Default>

c0000432
00:19:43.390 --> 00:19:44.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He'd come with you, of course.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:19:46.150 --> 00:19:47.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN'S BROTHER]
Understood.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:19:48.650 --> 00:19:52.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Heiter, I deeply
appreciate the offer,</b></Default>

c0000435
00:19:52.860 --> 00:19:54.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but my life here is just fine.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:19:54.650 --> 00:19:56.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More than that,
it's what my brother knows.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:19:57.280 --> 00:20:00.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We tragically lost our parents
when he was young, you see.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:20:01.330 --> 00:20:02.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This village is his home.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:20:04.030 --> 00:20:06.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do thank you,
but I can't take away</b></Default>

c0000440
00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:07.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the one comfort he has left.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:20:11.380 --> 00:20:12.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Very well.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:20:14.210 --> 00:20:15.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're in a tricky situation.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:19.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose I wasted my time
by coming here.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:20:19.680 --> 00:20:21.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if I'm already
wasting time,</b></Default>

c0000445
00:20:22.350 --> 00:20:24.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>perhaps I'll talk
with your brother.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:20:24.260 --> 00:20:25.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The little ones
always get a kick</b></Default>

c0000447
00:20:25.940 --> 00:20:27.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>hearing the tales
of my adventures.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:20:28.940 --> 00:20:30.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My brother had a chance
to leave this village,</b></Default>

c0000449
00:20:30.900 --> 00:20:32.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but he stayed for me.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:37.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sein. Is that the reason you've
made yourself miserable?</b></Default>

c0000451
00:20:39.410 --> 00:20:40.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[slaps]
-[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000452
00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:43.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must see that you
and I are not the same!</b></Default>

c0000453
00:20:43.990 --> 00:20:45.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The decision to stay
was mine to make,</b></Default>

c0000454
00:20:45.830 --> 00:20:47.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I have never
in my life regretted it!</b></Default>

c0000455
00:20:48.290 --> 00:20:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't pretend that
you can say as much.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:20:50.460 --> 00:20:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How long do you intend
to regret your choice?</b></Default>

c0000457
00:20:53.540 --> 00:20:54.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For shame.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:20:54.670 --> 00:20:57.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000459
00:21:02.590 --> 00:21:05.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water gurgling]</b></Default>

c0000460
00:21:11.020 --> 00:21:12.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
I apologized to my brother.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:21:13.770 --> 00:21:14.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:21:15.400 --> 00:21:17.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't get the wrong idea
about the man.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:21:18.320 --> 00:21:19.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's kind as can be.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:21:20.570 --> 00:21:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's never once laid
a hand on me before.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:21:23.820 --> 00:21:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It just shows how strongly
he feels about this.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:21:27.210 --> 00:21:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I had never seen
that expression on his face.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:21:34.120 --> 00:21:36.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Frieren. You won.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:21:36.550 --> 00:21:38.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to become
an adventurer.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:21:39.180 --> 00:21:40.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My friend might need me.</b></Default>

c0000470
00:21:41.880 --> 00:21:43.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ten years isn't as long
as you think.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:21:44.970 --> 00:21:45.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well put.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:21:46.810 --> 00:21:49.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales and exhales]</b></Default>

c0000473
00:21:51.560 --> 00:21:53.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looking for him
is my main goal.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:55.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's the reason I'm doing this.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:21:56.150 --> 00:21:57.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll find that ape</b></Default>

c0000476
00:21:58.110 --> 00:22:00.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and make our ridiculous
childhood dreams come true.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:22:01.860 --> 00:22:03.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll travel with you for now,</b></Default>

c0000478
00:22:04.150 --> 00:22:05.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but hopefully,
I'll find him soon.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:22:07.080 --> 00:22:09.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Take that, fish!
-I'm impressed.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:22:09.790 --> 00:22:11.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000481
00:22:15.620 --> 00:22:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000482
00:22:18.300 --> 00:22:21.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're gonna miss you!
Be real careful, Sein!</b></Default>

c0000483
00:22:25.170 --> 00:22:27.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe I should've
asked this before,</b></Default>

c0000484
00:22:27.430 --> 00:22:28.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but where are you headed?</b></Default>

c0000485
00:22:29.180 --> 00:22:30.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heaven, of course.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:22:30.600 --> 00:22:32.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Is that someplace
you need to work to get to?</b></Default>

c0000487
00:22:33.480 --> 00:22:35.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll all end up
